><br />\n<br />\n環保 算啦 人類本身就係自私既動物  談環保 真係晒氣"},{"pid":"596b4f37db0bdfc4b57c2f791a46737a42f039f2","tid":258500,"uid":52542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>tesla係好環保好靜<br />\n但喺路上見唔少友揸得好9屎<br />\n真係幫唔落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靜就係靜<br />\n<br />\n但係環保？ 得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n換電個時 咪又係產生大量電子垃圾<br />\n<br />\n充電 d電點黎 ? 咪係唔環保咁產生d電出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環保 算啦 人類本身就係自私既動物  談環保 真係晒氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntesla 做到減廢氣，都屬於環保呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你睇外國charger可以用recycle fuel<br />\n香港做鬼到風力水力太陽能發電咩 <br />\n<br />\n喺香港好多揸tesla都揸得好衰<br />\n入停車場都要抽你頭，驚死你架車會用左佢個免費充電位咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a62e0763eea66e7e9febfbf168d62651f636eb3","tid":258500,"uid":71213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tesla 司機已經超越左benz 司機</blockquote><br />\n好多teslun都係benz轉會過去"},{"pid":"dd5f4c96896c7d79ace12270dca5d84c43b0401f","tid":258500,"uid":48460,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"多人用=無taste<br />\nGoodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想扮清泉都要俾啲心機諗過第二個有力啲例子"},{"pid":"ad919d7a7822195d01ef128ed7089907ea119d6b","tid":258500,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多人用=無taste<br />\nGoodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想扮清泉都要俾啲心機諗過第二個有力啲例子</blockquote><br />\n用iphone = 無taste<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5017a379a57bba882e03c9622bde61bf54733aaf","tid":258500,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多人用=無taste<br />\nGoodest logic<img src=\"/assets/fac